Resource Profile: CH IPS Composition

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-ips/StructureDefinition/ch-ips-composition Version: 1.0.0-ballot
Active as of 2024-05-17 Computable Name: ChIpsComposition

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This CH IPS profile for the resource Composition is derived from the corresponding CH Core profile and also ensures IPS conformity via the IPS profile referenced by the so-called imposeProfile extension.

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: CH IPS Document
  • Refer to this Resource Profile: CH IPS Composition
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Composition/UC1-Composition1
